==化学性质==

在高温高压下，顽火辉石（Oen，[[斜方晶系|斜方晶系]]）会发生相变，转变成斜顽辉石（Cen，[[单斜晶系|单斜晶系]]）<ref>[http://www.sciencedirect.com/science?_ob=ArticleURL&_udi=B6V6S-4CYGT45-1&_user=10&_coverDate=10/15/2004&_rdoc=1&_fmt=high&_orig=search&_sort=d&_docanchor=&view=c&_searchStrId=1410167541&_rerunOrigin=google&_acct=C000050221&_version=1&_urlVersion=0&_userid=10&md5=8b5ab8b628b968a685975152754ad3be Jennifer Kung, Baosheng Li, Takeyuki Uchida, Yanbin Wang, Daniel Neuville, Robert C. Liebermann(2004), "In situ measurements of sound velocities and densities across the orthopyroxene→high-pressure clinopyroxene transition in MgSiO3 at high pressure", Physics of the Earth and Planetary Interiors 147 (2004) 27–44]{{Dead link|date=2019年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>：

Oen <math>\rightarrow </math> Cen (>1000℃,6GPa)

在高温高压以及{{link-en|镁铝榴石|pyrope}}存在的情况下，辉石会溶于镁铝榴石形成[[固溶体|固溶体]]<ref>[http://www.sciencedirect.com/science?_ob=ArticleURL&_udi=B6V61-473FM2G-CY&_user=10&_coverDate=05/31/1967&_rdoc=1&_fmt=high&_orig=search&_sort=d&_docanchor=&view=c&_searchStrId=1410171383&_rerunOrigin=google&_acct=C000050221&_version=1&_urlVersion=0&_userid=10&md5=3bd466e6ac02c41601419bc69a097c25 A.E. Ringwood(1967)"The pyroxene-garnet transformation in the earth's mantle", Earth and Planetary Science Letters Volume 2, Issue 3,Pages 255-263]{{Dead link|date=2019年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。

